                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Snowden</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Foster</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-01-05"><hi rend="italic">January 5,
                            1893</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>My telegram referred to Mora and Caroline claims.</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Snowden.</hi></signed></closer>
                </div>
